 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Sssyx</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Join the market channel on your server and watch what people are offering to buy, espcially look for the stuff that people are willing to pay 1 - 1.5K pp for, this stuff sells quickly both to mains and people outfitting twinks. Elder Wolf Hide comes to mind, easy to get and goes for 1.5 - 2K on my server and sells very quickly.  Figure out which of those things you can camp yourself and go get them.  Figure out what other stuff you can camp while you travel to the places you are going to get the drops people are trying to buy and camp that stuff too.  Weight reducing bags should probably be your first expenditures too (there are a few you can camp and some you will need to buy.)</P><P>I'm not sure how much of it you could solo, but I think LGuk might be a good place to farm too.  Even if many of the items you get there only sell for 400 - 500pp, money adds up quickly if you sell a number of those items.</P><P>I'm not sure what race, but also consider binding in the Firepot room.  It is hard to beat the ease of travel it provides as you can port cities not far from many great farming spots to keep the pace up.</P><P><b>I AM the angry leeezurd!</b></P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22254" target="_blank" target="_blank">Sssyx Syxyx</a></P><P><a href="mailto:sssyx@mmdog.com">sssyx@mmdog.com</a></P><P></font></td>
